A rooftop fitness center at dawn in a high-rise Asian hotel, seen from inside looking out through floor-to-ceiling windows. Modern exercise equipment silhouetted against a sprawling cityscape of skyscrapers bathed in golden morning light. Steam rises from a swimming pool on the terrace outside. In the foreground, a glass bowl of fresh tropical fruits—mangosteen, dragon fruit, and rambutan—sits on a sleek counter beside a neatly folded towel. The scene conveys luxury, wellness, and the solitary rhythm of a frequent traveler's morning routine. Photorealistic style with warm cinematic lighting and slight lens flare from the rising sun.
